Created 1.4.1986 from the parishes of Charles and High Bray. See

    Brayford. See also Table 2, note (b).

    Newton Tracey.

Renamed 12.1.1976 to become the parish of Lynton & Lynmouth.

Created 12.1.1976 by renaming the parish of Lynton. See also

    Newton Tracey.
